s done since Raging Bull.”</p>  <figure class=\"element element-image\" data-media-id=\"49f09cd89ea3a7a846f0352687ea983d3436660e\"> <img src=\"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/13/1426264062451/96be7218-b120-4f76-8e45-6dbcbb8a2c34-460x276.jpeg\" alt=\"Mike Tyson in September 2014.\" width=\"460\" height=\"276\" class=\"gu-image\" /> <figcaption> <span class=\"element-image__caption\">Mike Tyson in September 2014.</span> <span class=\"element-image__credit\">Photograph: Alex Menendez/Getty Images</span> </figcaption> </figure>  <p>In the same interview, Foxx also says that he wants Tyson’s children to run up to him and say ‘Daddy’ because of how similar the pair will look. There hasn’t been an official announcement as yet but it follows <a href=\"http://variety.com/2014/film/news/jamie-foxx-terrence-winter-mike-tyson-1201266853/\">word that Boardwalk Empire writer Terrence Winter will be working on the screenplay and Foxx’s manager Rick Yorn will produce</a>. </p> <p>Martin Scorsese is currently filming Silence, a historical drama starring Liam Neeson, and had been linked to a Frank Sinatra biopic. Jamie Foxx was last seen in the remake of Annie and as Electro in The Amazing Spider-Man 2. </p>","headline":"Raging Foxx: Jamie says Martin Scorsese will direct him as Mike Tyson","trailText":"Oscar winning actor reveals that the Raging Bull director will be on towel duties for planned boxer biopic","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2015/3/13/1426262977980/68f8f2c7-30c0-4685-882b-d8c1fe75fc64-140x84.jpeg","wordcount":"234","commentable":"true","byline":"Benjamin Lee","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2015-03-16T16:45:00+00:00"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/mar/13/jamie-foxx-martin-scorsese-mike-tyson-movie","apiUrl":"http://content.guardianapis.com/film/2015/mar/13/jamie-foxx-martin-scorsese-mike-tyson-movie","sectionName":"Film","tags":[{"id":"film/ja